a:10:{s:7:"content";s:2061:"        




<div class="content-view-full">
    <div class="class-frontpage leftcolumn norightcolumn">

    <div class="columns-frontpage float-break">
        <div class="left-column-position">
            <div class="left-column">
            <!-- Content: START -->
                   
<p>Welcome to Hacker News [Delta] the social networking news website clone where the news is user submitted and moderated. Users are&nbsp;empowered to decide what makes it to the homepage via user submitted voting and moderation.</p><a name="eztoc355120_0_1" id="eztoc355120_0_1"></a><h3>Hacker News Delta is Open Source!</h3><p>We support users with a shared interest in building their own open source social networks and web page blogs with our software based on the Exponential (CMS).</p><p>HackerNewsDelta.com, Hacker News [Delta] is free software licensed under the gnu GPLv2 or later and released to the general public as hackerNewsClone and diggClone projects.</p><p>Available now to everyone wanting to offer Hacker News / Digg / Reddit style content voting and interaction for their own website or community online.</p><a name="eztoc355120_0_1_1" id="eztoc355120_0_1_1"></a><h4>Upcoming</h4>
<ul>

<li>Source code publishing on <a href="https://github.com/se7enxweb/sevenx_hackerNewsDelta" target="_self">GitHub</a>.</li>

<li>Source code installation instruction publication on GitHub.</li>

</ul>
            <!-- Content: END -->
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="center-column-position">
            <div class="center-column float-break">
                <div class="overflow-fix">
                <!-- Content: START -->
                    
